\id MIC
\h Mixa
\toc1 Mixa
\toc2 Mixa
\toc3 Mixa
\mt1 Mixa
\c 1
\s1 Řḥukm x Samarya d Urcalim
\m 
\v 1 Awař n SIDI i dd-yusin ɣar Mixa, Amuracti, deg wussan n Yutam d Aḥaz d Ḥizqiya, ijeǧiden n Yahuda, \add awař\add* i iẓra x Samarya d Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Irm. 26:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Sřem-dd, marra kenniw, \add a\add* řegnus,
\m iřim tfetnem, \add a cem\add*, tammurt
\m d uɛemmar nnes!
\m Sidi inu, SIDI,
\m ad yiři d acehhad xawem,
\m Sidi inu zi Zzawect nnes iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Aɛwd. 32:1; Ica. 1:2\x*
\m 
\v 3 Maɣar xzarem, SIDI iffeɣ-dd
\m zeg wemcan nnes \add n tzeddiɣt\add*,
\m u Netta ad dd-ihwa
\m u ad iṣurf x řegɛudi n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Aɛwd. 32:13; 33:29; Izhd. 115:3; Ica. 26:21, Ɛam. 4:13\x*
\m 
\v 4 Idurar ad fesyen sadu nnes,
\m u tiɣzurin ad ttwabḍant,
\m am ccmeɛ zzat i wudem n tmessi,
\m am waman nni dd-ittwafarrɣen
\m zi teysart. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Řqḍ. 5:4; Izhd. 18:8, 10; Izhd. 68:3, 9; Izhd. 97:5; Ɛam. 9:5\x*
\m 
\v 5 Aya marra \add ittemsar\add*
\m zi ssibbet n uxeṭṭu n Yaɛqub,
\m u zi ssibbet n ddnub
\m n taddart n Israil.
\m Min iǧan d xeṭṭu n Yaɛqub?
\m Ma war \add iǧi\add* d Samarya?
\m U min ǧan d řegɛudi n Yahuda?
\m Ma war \add teǧi\add* d Urcalim?
\m 
\v 6 Necc ad arreɣ Samarya
\m d řxarbet deg iyyar,
\m d amarjeɛ mani ɣa ẓẓun tazayart,
\m u Necc ad nḍareɣ iẓra nnes di teɣzurt,
\m u ad ɛarriɣ x dsusa nnes.
\m 
\v 7 Marra řexyařat nnes ineqcen
\m ad ttwaředǧent
\m u marra řmunet nnes n farq-ccɣeř
\m ad tt sscemḍen s tmessi,
\m u marra řexyařat nnes ineqcen
\m ad tent areddǧeɣ Necc,
\m maɣar nettat tyarew i-tent
\m zi řmunet n farq-ccɣeř,
\m u nitenti ad dd-dewřent ɛawed
\m d řmunet n farq-ccɣeř.”
\b
\s1 Acḍan ameqqran n Mixa
\m 
\v 8 “X uya ad ceḍneɣ u ad wteɣ agejdur,
\m ad uyureɣ s řeḥfa d aɛaryan,
\m ad ssmiɛweɣ am wuccanen n řexřa,
\m u ad sɣuyeɣ am yessis n nnɛamet. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Ayub 30:29\x*
\m 
\v 9 Maɣar iyezzimen nnes neqqen,
\m maɣar \add aya\add* yusa-dd ař Yahuda,
\m iwesseɛ \add řḥukm\add* ař tiwwura n řgens inu,
\m ař Urcalim.
\m 
\v 10 War ttbarrḥem ca man aya di Jat,
\m war tᵉttrum, war xas nessiwiř.
\m Di Bayt-Li’afra zuzzareɣ \add a\add*cař
\m x yixef inu. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Ṣm. 1:20; Irm. 6:26\x*
\m 
\v 11 Ɛdu, cem tenni izeddɣen di Cafir,
\m d aɛaryan u s řeḥya.
\m Tenni izeddɣen di Ṣanan war teffiɣ ca.
\m Taɣuyyit n wecḍan n Bayt-Ha-Iṭṣil
\m tekkes zzaywem abeddi nnes akidwem. \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Ica. 47:3\x*
\m 
\v 12 Maɣar tenni izeddɣen di Marut,
\m tᵉtteqnunnuy ɣar marra tiɣemmura
\m di ṭṭweɛ n řxar,
\m \add minzi\add* aqa ihwa-dd řɣar n SIDI,
\m ař tawwart n Urcalim. \f ◼ \fr 1:12 \fk Marut\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tarzugi’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:12 \xt Ɛam. 3:6\x*
\m 
\v 13 Ḥezzmem iysan n tazřa zzat i ukarru,
\m \add a cem\add*, tenni izeddɣen di Laxic!
\m Nettat d beṭṭu n ddenb
\m n yeǧis n Ṣihyun,
\m maɣar dayek ttwafen ixeṭṭan n Israil.
\m 
\v 14 S uya ewc arriɣaluten n umsebḍi
\m i Muracat-Jat!
\m Tudrin n Akzib ad dewřent d řɣecc
\m i ijeǧiden n Israil.
\m 
\v 15 Ɛawed Necc ad am dd-awyeɣ awrit,
\m \add a cem\add* tenni izeddɣen di Marica!
\m Aɛuǧi n Israil ad dd-yas
\m ař ɣar Ɛadullam.
\m 
\v 16 Egg ixef nnem d taqeccart
\m u ḥeff i ixef nnem
\m di ssibbet n iḥenjiren nnem iɛizzen.
\m Arr taqeccart nnem d tameqqrant
\m amecnaw agider,
\m minzi ttwawyen zzayem
\m ɣar tmeḥbast.”
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Iɛřamen i Israil u i řḥukkam nnes
\m 
\v 1 “Uct x yinni ittxemmamen
\m di řmuɛṣiyyet
\m u \add x yinni\add* ittxemmamen
\m di řɣar di qamat nsen.
\m Ɣar tuffut ad t ggen,
\m maɣar afus nsen
\m \add dayes\add* aṭṭas n tzemmar.
\m 
\v 2 Nitni mmeẓřen deg iyyaren
\m uca ttkeccḍen ten ɛawed,
\m uřa d tudrin, uca ttᵉṭṭfen tent.
\m Ammu i ggin nitni s řexcunet
\m i weryaz u i taddart nnes,
\m \add wah, i kuř\add* aryaz u i tesɣart nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Ica. 5:8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 3 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI:
\m Xzar, Necc twenniɣ ijj n řɣar
\m x řaǧ-a, i zi war tzemmarem
\m ad tjebdem irawen nwem,
\m u \add i zi\add* war tzemmaren
\m ad tuyurem \add ɛad\add* s uɛeffar,
\m maɣar \add ad tiři\add* d ict n řweqt taɛeffant.\x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Ɛam. 5:13\x*
\m 
\v 4 Deg wass nni ad xawem ssgeɛɛden
\m ijj n lmatal
\m u ad ɣennjen ijj n yeẓri n wecḍan
\m am ttcetcan,
\m u ad inin: Neccin nettwareddeǧ qaɛ!
\m Netta yarra tasɣart n řgens inu
\m \add ɣar wenneɣni.\add*
\m Mammec tt iksi zzayi?
\m Netta iwca iyyaren nneɣ
\m i wenni dd-iffɣen zeg webrid!
\m 
\v 5 S uya war ɣarek ittiři uřa d ijjen
\m wenni i ɣa inḍaren afiřu \add n řeqyas\add*
\m ɛlaḥsab taqedduḥt
\m deg wegraw \add n řgens\add* n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Aɛwd. 32:8, 9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 “‘War ssuffuɣem awař
\m \add ammu\add* s ukuffu!’,
\m \add ammu\add* i ssawařen nitni
\m am ssuffuɣen kuffu.
\m ‘X man aya war zemmaren nitni
\m ad ssuffɣen awař s ukuffu!’
\m \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tiři řefḍiḥet
\m war tᵉttwakkess! \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Ica. 30:10; Ɛam. 7:16\x*
\m 
\v 7 \add A kenniw,\add* taddart n Yaɛqub,
\m ma izemmar ad ittwanna aya?
\m ‘Ma ijja ca Arruḥ n SIDI war t iggi?’
\m niɣ: ‘Ma tina d timegga nnes?’
\m Ma war tteggen wawařen inu řxar
\m i yinni igguren s tsegda?
\m 
\v 8 \add Maca ɛad\add* idennaḍ ikkar řgens inu
\m am yijj n řeɛdu.
\m Tqeřɛem arruḍ d upartessu
\m zeg imsebriden iqefřen
\m i war tt ittrijin,
\m inni ittɛiffen umenɣi.
\m 
\v 9 Kenniw tessuffuɣem
\m timɣarin n řgens inu
\m zi taddart nsent iɛizzen.
\m Iḥenjiren nnes tekksem asen
\m talwizt inu i řebda.
\m 
\v 10 Kkarem u aggʷejem,
\m minzi wa war iǧi d amcan n arraḥet!
\m Maɣar aqa \add tammurt\add* tᵉttwassexmej,
\m ad tawi areddeǧ,
\m \add wah\add* ijj n nnɛi n ureddeǧ.
\m 
\v 11 Mařa ca n ijj iḍeffar asemmiḍ,
\m iqqar ixarriqen, \add uca iqqar:\add*
\m ‘Necc ad ac ssuffɣeɣ awařen s ukuffu
\m di ṭṭweɛ n binu d ccrab!’
\m aqa netta igga
\m \add axmi netta d anabi\add* n řgens
\m nni issuffuɣen awařen s ukuffu.”
\b
\m 
\v 12 “S tidett, \add a\add* Yaɛqub,
\m Necc ad cek ksiɣ \add ɣari\add* qaɛ,
\m nican Necc ad ssmuneɣ
\m min iqqimen zi Israil.
\m Ad ten ssmuneɣ am wuǧi n Buṣra,
\m am ict n tḥimart di řwesṭ n trekkwast
\m ad din yiři ijj n uɛurric n iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Ica. 34:6; 63:1; Irm. 48:24; 49:13, 22, Ɛam. 1:12. \x*
\m 
\v 13 Amfeǧeq ad izwar zzat i wudem nsen,
\m nitni ad feǧqen u ad ɛdun x tewwart,
\m u ad zzayes dd-ffɣen.
\m Ajeǧid nsen ad izwar
\m zzat i uɣembub nsen,
\m u SIDI ɣar uzeǧif nsen.”
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Řḥukkam d inabiyyen n Israil ttfecřen
\m 
\v 1 “\add Xenni\add* nniɣ necc:
\b
\m ‘Sřem, \add a kenniw,\add* izeǧifen n Yaɛqub,
\m u \add kenniw\add*, řḥukkam n taddart n Israil!
\m Ma war ittxeṣṣi i kenniw
\m ad tessnem tasɣart?
\m 
\v 2 Nitni carrhen min icnan
\m u ttexsen min iǧan d aɛeffan!
\m Nitni kksen asen tiřmect
\m uřa d aysum x iɣsan nsen.
\m 
\v 3 \add Wah,\add* aqa aten d yinni ittetten
\m aysum n řgens inu
\m uca kksen asen tiřmect
\m uca ttareẓẓan iɣsan nsen.
\m Nitni ttbezzaɛen ten am di marmita,
\m am weysum deg uṭenjir.”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Řexdenni ad sɣuyen ɣar SIDI,
\m \add maca\add* war xasen dd-ittarri.
\m Ad xasen iffar udem nnes di řweqt nni,
\m zi ssibbet n řɣar i iggin.”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI i inabiyyen
\m inni ittɣarran řgens inu,
\m inni umi ɣarsen ɛad min di
\m i ɣa izeɛfen s teɣmas nsen,
\m ad řaɣan ‘Řehna!’,
\m \add maca\add* ḍidd n wenni war d asen ittegg
\m walu deg uqemmum nsen,
\m ad xas qeddsen ijj n umenɣi. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Mixa 2:11\x*
\m 
\v 6 S uya ad xawem dd-tewḍa ǧiřet,
\m břa řewḥiy,
\m u \add ad\add* xawem \add dd-iwḍa\add* taǧest
\m břa tagezzant.
\m Ad teɣři tfuct x inabiyyen
\m u ad ibbarcen wass tiwa nsen. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Irm. 15:9; Yuw. 2:10; Ɛam. 8:9\x*
\m 
\v 7 Imwařawen ad seḍḥan,
\m u igezzanen ad dewřen
\m zewɣwen s řeḥya,
\m u nitni marra ad řeḥḥfen acřaɣem
\m ɣar uyencic,
\m minzi twarrit n AREBBI
\m war dd-tᵉttis ca.
\m 
\v 8 Maca necc ccureɣ s jjehd
\m n Arruḥ n SIDI,
\m u s řḥeqq d teryast,
\m ḥima ad barrḥeɣ i Yaɛqub
\m x uxeṭṭu nnes
\m u i Israil x ddenb nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Sřem xenni ɣar man aya,
\m \add a\add* izeǧifen n taddart n Yaɛqub
\m u kenniw imeqqranen
\m n taddart n Israil,
\m inni icarrhen řḥeqq,
\m u ssfarraɣen marra min iǧan iseggem, \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Ɛam. 5:7; 6:12\x*
\m 
\v 10 inni ibennan Ṣihyun s idammen,
\m u Urcalim s řɣecc. \x ◘ \xo 3:10 \xt Ḥiz. 22:27; Ṣaf. 3:3\x*
\m 
\v 11 Izeǧifen nnes ttḍebbaran
\m ddɛawi i arrecwet,
\m ikehhanen nnes sseřmaden s řmunet,
\m u ikehhanen nnes
\m ttgezzanen s tmenyat.
\m Aqa nitni ttcařen x SIDI xmi qqaren:
\m ‘Ma war iǧi SIDI di řwest nneɣ?
\m War d aneɣ iřeqqef řɣar.’
\m 
\v 12 S uya, aqa-tt zzaywem,
\m aqa ad carzen Ṣihyun am yijj n yeyyar,
\m ad tedweř \add tendint n\add* Urcalim
\m d ict n řxarbet,
\m u adrar n Taddart d řegɛudi n wezɣar.” \f ◼ \fr 3:12 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Mixa 3:12\x*
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Tageldit i dd ɣa yasen zi Ṣihyun
\m 
\v 1 “Deg uneggar n wussan ad imsar,
\m aqa adrar n Taddart n SIDI
\m ad ibedd imten
\m x tqiccet n idurar.
\m Ad yiři yuɛřa x tewririn,
\m uca řegnus ad ɣares dd-azzřen. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Ica. 2:2-5\x*
\m 
\v 2 Aṭṭas n řegnus ad geɛɛden, ad inin:
\m “Jjem aneɣ ad ngeɛɛed
\m ɣar wedrar n SIDI
\m u ɣar Taddart n AREBBI n Yaɛqub,
\m ḥima ad aneɣ isseřmed
\m zeg ibriden nnes,
\m ad nuyur neccin deg imesraq nnes,
\m minzi zi Ṣihyun ad dd-teffeɣ Ccariɛa
\m u awař n SIDI zi Urcalim.
\m 
\v 3 Netta ad icarreɛ jar řegnus imɣaren
\m u ad iseggem řegnus
\m nni ɣar iǧa tizemmar timeqqranin,
\m ɛad uřa d \add řegnus\add* iggʷejen.
\m Nitni ad ggen řesyuf nsen d dduzan
\m u fřitcat nsen d řemwas n wezbar.
\m War issgiɛɛid uřa d ijj n řgens
\m ɛad ssif x wenneɣni,
\m u nitni war řemmden \add ɛad\add* amenɣi.
\m 
\v 4 Nitni ad qqimen,
\m kuř ijj sadu tzayart nnes
\m u sadu wartu n tazart nnes,
\m uca uřa d ijjen ad \add ten\add* issnexřeɛ,
\m maɣar aqemmum n SIDI n řɛeskarat
\m aqa inna t.” \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt 1 Ij. 5:5, Zak. 3:10\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Minzi marra řegnus ad uyuren,
\m kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* deg yisem n arebbi nnes,
\m maca neccin ad nuyur deg Yisem n SIDI,
\m AREBBI nneɣ,
\m i řebda qaɛ.”
\b
\s1 SIDI ad issenjem Ṣihyun
\m 
\v 6 “Deg wass nni, iqqar SIDI,
\m Necc ad yarweɣ min iqejdḥen,
\m u ad \add ɣari\add* ssmuneɣ min x uzzřen,
\m u wi di ggiɣ Necc řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Aɛwd. 30:3, 4, 5\x*
\m 
\v 7 Min iqejdḥen ad t ggeɣ d řbaqi,
\m uřa min ittwaɛarrnen ɣar řaggʷaj,
\m \add ad t ggeɣ\add* d ijj n řgens
\m s tzemmar d tameqqrant,
\m uca SIDI ad xasen yiři d Ajeǧid
\m x wedrar n Ṣihyun,
\m zi řexxu ař řebda. \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Dan. 7:14; Ṣaf. 3:19; Lk. 1:33\x*
\m 
\v 8 I cem, Migdal-Ɛidr,
\m \add a cem,\add* tawrirt n yeǧis n Ṣihyun!
\m ad ɣarem dd-tas,
\m \add wah,\add* ad \add ɣarem\add* dd-tas řeḥkamet
\m tenni \add i tuɣa iǧan\add* deg umezwaru,
\m tageldit n yeǧis n Urcalim.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Řexxu \add maca\add*,
\m mayemmi tesɣuyyud \add ammu\add* s jjehd?
\m Ma war ɣarem iǧi ujeǧid?
\m Ma ittwahellek umcawar nnem,
\m aqa iṭṭef i cem řeḥriq
\m am n yict n temɣart ittarwen? \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Irm. 8:19\x*
\m 
\v 10 Ɣnes u tɛebbzed,
\m \add a cem,\add* yeǧis n Ṣihyun,
\m am ict n temɣart ittarwen.
\m Maɣar \add waxxa\add* řexxu
\m ad teffɣed zi tendint,
\m ad tzedɣed deg iyyar,
\m uca ad dd-tased ař Babil.
\m \add Maca\add* din ad tnejmed,
\m dinni ad cem ifekk SIDI
\m zeg ufus n řɛedyan nnem.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 Řexxu \add maca\add* munen xak
\m aṭṭas n řegnus.
\m Nitni qqaren: ‘Nettat ad tᵉttwaɛarra!’
\m Tiṭṭawin nneɣ ad ẓarent Ṣihyun.
\m 
\v 12 Nitni war ssinen inwayen n SIDI,
\m u war fehhmen ca ccwar nnes!
\m Maɣar Netta iksi ten \add ɣares\add*
\m am tqebbiḍin n imendi deg unedrar.” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Irm. 51:33\x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Kkar, tessarewted,
\m \add a cem,\add* yeǧis n Ṣihyun,
\m maɣar Necc ad arreɣ
\m yicc nnem d uzzař,
\m u ad am ggeɣ ticeḍyin nnem zi nnḥas,
\m u cem ad třebzed aṭṭas n řegnus
\m u Necc ad ḥarrmeɣ
\m takeccaḍt nsen marra i SIDI,
\m uřa d agřa nsen i Sidi n marra tammurt. \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt Zak. 4:14; 6:5\x*
\m 
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, řeḥmem
\m ijjen ɣar wenneɣni,
\m \add a cem\add* yeǧis
\m n ict n bandiyya \add n ixewwanen\add*!
\m Netta iḥeṣṣar aneɣ.
\m Nitni ad ccaten řqaḍi n Israil
\m x uqabsi s ijj n weɛmud.”
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Řḥakem i dd ɣa yasen zi Bayt-Lahm
\m 
\v 1 “U cek, Bayt-Laḥm Ifrata,
\m \add waxxa\add* cek d ameẓyan
\m ařami \add war tzemmared\add*
\m ad tiřid jar řuřuf n Yahuda,
\m aqa zzayek i dd ɣa iffeɣ Netta i Necc,
\m maḥend ad yiři d Řḥakem x Israil.
\m Abani nnes aqa-t zi mecḥař uya,
\m zeg wussan n řebda. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Mt. 2:6; Yḥ. 7:42\x*
\m 
\v 2 S uya Netta ad ten isellem
\m ař řweqt nni,
\m aqa tenni i ɣa yarwen, aqa turuw-dd.
\m Xenni ad dd-idweř řbaqi n yaytmas,
\m \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 3 Netta ad ibedd \add dinni\add*
\m uca ad yarwes di jjehd n SIDI,
\m di řuɛřa n Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes.
\m Nitni ad zedɣen \add dinni\add*,
\m maɣar Netta ad yiři d ameqqran
\m ař ineggura n temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 5:3 \fk ař ineggura n temmurt\ft - ixs ad yini ‘ař ineggura n ddunect’.\f*
\m 
\v 4 Wanita ad yiři d Řehna.”
\b
\m “Xmi dd ɣa yas Accur ɣar temmurt nneɣ,
\m u xmi dd ɣa yadef ɣar řeqṣur nneɣ,
\m xenni ad as nesseřqa
\m sebɛa n imeksawen
\m d tmenya n ayt n jjehd zi midden. \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Ica. 9:5\x*
\m 
\v 5 Nitni ad ḥḍan
\m x temmurt n Accur s ssif
\m u tammurt n Nimrud di tewwura nnes.
\m \add Ammu\add* Netta ad aneɣ issenjem
\m zeg \add ufus\add* n Accur,
\m xmi dd ɣa yas wanita
\m ɣar temmurt nneɣ
\m u xmi dd ɣa yadef
\m ɣar wudem n temmurt nneɣ.”
\b
\s1 Řbaqi n Yaɛqub
\m 
\v 6 “Řbaqi n Yaɛqub ad yiři
\m di řwesṭ n řegnus
\m amecnaw nnda n SIDI,
\m amecnaw tiddumin x wefsu \add aziza,\add*
\m wenni war ixezzaren
\m ɣar uřa d ijj n weryaz
\m u war ittrijin tarwa n bnadem.
\m 
\v 7 Řbaqi n Yaɛqub ad yiři jar řegnus,
\m di řwesṭ n řegnus,
\m amecnaw ayrad jar řmař n yezɣar,
\m amecnaw ayrad d ameẓyan
\m jar tḥimriwin n wuǧi,
\m wenni, xmi ɣa iɛdu,
\m iɛeffes u ittcarrag
\m uca war din uřa d ijj i ɣa ifekken. \f ◼ \fr 5:7 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\m 
\v 8 Afus nnec ad yiři ittwassgeɛɛed
\m sennej i yinni i cek iḥeṣṣaren,
\m uca marra řɛedyan nnec
\m ad ttwamḥan.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Ad imsar deg wass nni,
\m \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI,
\m aqa Necc ad teḥḥiɣ iysan nnec
\m zi řwesṭ nnec
\m u ad sshellkeɣ ikarruten nnec. \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Ḥuc. 14:4\x*
\m 
\v 10 Ad mḥiɣ tineddam zi temmurt nnec,
\m ad hedmeɣ marra lqelɛat nnec.
\m 
\v 11 Necc ad qeḍɛeɣ taseḥḥart nnec
\m zeg ufus nnem
\m u war ɣarek ttiřin ɛad ibezgawen.
\m 
\v 12 Řexyařat nnem ineqcen
\m d imayḍuten nnec \add iqeddsen\add*
\m ad \add ten\add* mḥiɣ zi řwest nnec,
\m ḥima war tᵉttbendaqed ɛad
\m i řxedmet n ifassen nnec.
\m 
\v 13 u tirebbin nnec n cwarti
\m ad tent teḥḥiɣ zi řwesṭ nnec.
\b
\m \add Maca\add* ad hedmeɣ řɛedyan nnec
\m 
\v 14 uca ad ntaqmeɣ s weɣḍab u s wesɛar
\m x řegnus nni war \add ittexsen\add* ad sřen.”
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Acetci n SIDI x řgens nnes u x Urcalim
\m 
\v 1 “Sřem xenni min iqqar SIDI:
\m Kkar, carreɛ zzat i wudem n idurar,
\m u ejj tiwririn ad sřent i tmijja nnec!
\m 
\v 2 Sřem, \add a\add* idurar, i ddeɛwet n SIDI,
\m \add uřa d kenniw\add*, dsusa imetnen n temmurt,
\m minzi SIDI ɣares ict n ddeɛwet
\m ak-d řgens nnes
\m Netta iggur ɣar taddart n ccreɛ
\m ak-d Israil.” \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Ḥuc. 4:1\x*
\b
\m 
\v 3 “\add A\add* řgens inu, min d ac ggiɣ,
\m u s manten i zi cek ssiḥřeɣ?
\m Cehhed ḍidd inu!
\m 
\v 4 Necc nedheɣ cek zi temmurt n Miṣra,
\m zi taddart n tesmuɣi.
\m Necc ssekkeɣ-dd Musa
\m d Harun d Maryam
\m zzat i uɣembub nnec. \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt Uf. 12:51; 14:30; 20:2\x*
\m 
\v 5 \add A\add* řgens inu, fekkar mliḥ di \add řɣar\add*
\m i \add tuɣa\add* inekkʷa ad yegg Balak,
\m ajeǧid n Mu’ab,
\m u di min xas dd-yarra Bilɛam,
\m mmis n Baɛur
\m \add u di min imsaren\add* zi Ciṭṭim ař Jiljal,
\m ḥima ad tessned
\m timegga iseggden n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Řxř. 22:5; 23:7; 25; Yac. 5\x*
\b
\s1 Min ixs SIDI zi řgens nnes?
\m 
\v 6 “S min zi ɣa raḥeɣ
\m ad mmeřqiɣ ak-d SIDI,
\m ad aḍareɣ zzat i Arebbi yuɛřan?
\m Ma ad raḥeɣ ad t mmeřqiɣ
\m s tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ,
\m niɣ s iɛejmiyyen n ijj n useggʷas? \f ◼ \fr 6:6 \fk iɛejmiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*
\m 
\v 7 Ma ad yarḍa SIDI
\m s řuřuf n icarriyyen,
\m s ɛecra n řuřuf n tɣezratin n zzect?
\m Ma ad wceɣ amenzu inu i uxeṭṭu inu,
\m řɣiǧet n uɛeddis inu
\m i ddnub n řeɛmar inu?
\m 
\v 8 Netta issargeb i cek, \add a\add* bnadem,
\m min icnan,
\m u min zzayek ittettar SIDI,
\m aqa ad tegged řxar,
\m ad texsed tamexsiwt icewwaren,
\m u ad tuyured ak-d AREBBI nnec
\m s uwaḍeɛ!” \x ◘ \xo 6:8 \xt Aɛwd. 10:12\x*
\b
\s1 Areddeǧ n iɛeffanen
\m 
\v 9 “Tmijja n SIDI tᵉttřaɣa i tendint.
\m Isem nnec ittawi-dd ufekki.
\m Sřem i weɛmud
\m u ɣar wenni t-i-dd issekken!
\m 
\v 10 Ma din ɛad řexzin ccuren s řɣar
\m di taddart n uɛeffan
\m uřa d ijj n nnɛi n \add řmud n\add* ifa inqeṣ?
\m 
\v 11 Ma izemmar ad iřiɣ d amezdag
\m s řmizanat n řɣar,
\m u s yict n tecyart \add teccur\add*
\m s řewznat iɣeccen? \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Ḥuc. 12:8\x*
\m 
\v 12 Ayt bu-wagřa nnes aqa ccuren s lɛunf,
\m uřa d imezdaɣ nnes qqaren ixarriqen
\m u iřes nsen aqa ittɣecca
\m deg uqemmum nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt Irm. 9:7\x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Xenni Necc aqa jarḥeɣ cem s teyyita,
\m aqa tᵉttwareddǧed
\m zi ssibbet n ddnub nnem.
\m 
\v 14 Ad tecced, \add maca\add* war tᵉttjiwined,
\m u ad dayem yiři řaẓ di daxeř nnem.
\m Ad teffɣed,
\m \add maca\add* war tnejjmed,
\m u min inejmen,
\m ad t sseɛduɣ i ssif. \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt Ḥuc. 4:10\x*
\m 
\v 15 Ggur ad tzarɛed, \add maca\add* war tmejjared,
\m ad teddzed aẓemmur,
\m \add maca\add* war tdehhned ixef nnem s zzect
\m \add ad tẓemmed\add* uřa d binu n jdid \add zeg uḍiř\add*,
\m \add maca\add* war tᵉssessed binu. \x ◘ \xo 6:15 \xt Aɛwd. 28:38; Ḥag. 1:6\x*
\m 
\v 16 \add Maɣar\add* řgens iḥeṭṭan tiweṣṣa n Ɛumri
\m u marra timegga \add tiɛeffanin\add*
\m n taddart n Axab,
\m u kenniw tḍeffarem řecwar nsen,
\m ařami cem i ɣa yarreɣ
\m d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ
\m uřa d imezdaɣ nnes i usemẓi.
\m \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tarbum řḥegra n řgens inu.” \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt 1 Ij. 16:25, 26,30-34\x*
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Mixa iẓra tuɛeffna i iǧan di řgens
\m 
\v 1 “Uct inu, maɣar aqa ayi ɣari
\m amecnaw ɣar tmeyra n tini n unebdu,
\m amecnaw ɣar twařa wiss tnayen
\m n weřqaḍ n uḍiř:
\m war din uřa d ijj n uzekkun n uḍiř
\m i macca,
\m war din iǧi uřa d ijj n řbacur qbeř řweqt
\m i dayes meẓri řeɛmar inu.
\m 
\v 2 Ameddukkař i dayes
\m tamexsiwt icewwaren
\m war iqqim di temmurt,
\m uca war din uřa d ijj n uṣebḥan
\m jar iwdan.
\m Nitni marra ttḥaman x idammen,
\m ijjen iyemmar wenneɣni s tracca. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Izhd. 12:2; Ḥuc. 4:1\x*
\m 
\v 3 Ifassen nsen wejden s tnayen
\m maḥend ad ggen řɣar.
\m Řḥakem ittar u řqaḍi \add ittegg i-tt\add*
\m di ṭṭweɛ n uxeǧeṣ,
\m u wenni ameqqran issawař
\m \add ɛlaḥsab\add* meẓri \add aɛeffan\add* n řeɛmar nnes
\m u \add ammu\add* i ssfarɣen nitni tamesřact. \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Mixa 2:1; 3:11\x*
\m 
\v 4 Wenni zzaysen d aṣebḥan aṭṭas
\m \add aqa-t\add* am yijj n cbarq n isennanen,
\m wenni d aṣdiq n wuř qaɛ \add zzaysen\add*
\m \add aqa-t\add* mahu x ijj n wefray n cbarq
\m ak-d isennanen.
\m Ass n iɛessasen nnec,
\m \add ass n\add* uxeǧeṣ, yusa-dd.
\m Řexxu ad nxeřɛen.”
\b
\s1 Mixa ad iraja asenjem n Arebbi
\m 
\v 5 “War tumined deg ijj n umeddukkeř,
\m war tᵉttecřed
\m x umeddukkeř \add nnec\add* iɛizzen.
\m Ḥḍa tiwwura n uqemmum nnec
\m zi tenni iǧan ɣar weḥsin nnec.
\m 
\v 6 Maɣar mmis isseḥqara babas,
\m yeǧis tᵉttḍadda yemmas,
\m tasřit x lallas,
\m řɛedyan n ijj n weryaz
\m aqa d aytbab n taddart nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Ḥiz. 22:7; Mt. 10:21, 35, 36; Lk. 12:53\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 “\add Maca\add* necc ad xzareɣ ɣar SIDI,
\m ad rajiɣ AREBBI n usenjem inu.
\m AREBBI inu ad ɣari dd-iseř.”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “War d ayi sfarreḥ,
\m \add a cem\add* tamɣart nni d řeɛdu inu!
\m Maɣar mařa wḍiɣ, ad kkareɣ ɛawed,
\m mařa qqimeɣ di taǧest,
\m ad yiři SIDI d tafawt i necc.
\m 
\v 9 Necc ad ksiɣ asxeḍ n SIDI,
\m minzi necc xḍiɣ akides,
\m ař xafi i ɣa iwwet Netta x ddeɛwet inu
\m u ad ayi yaɣ tasɣart inu.
\m Netta ad ayi issuffeɣ ɣar tfawt,
\m necc ad ẓareɣ tasegda nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:9 \xt Izhd. 9:5-6; Izhd. 43:1; Irm. 50:34\x*
\m 
\v 10 Tamɣart tenni d řeɛdu inu
\m ad tẓar aya.
\m Mři d as i ɣa tdeř řeḥya
\m i tenni d ayi iqqaren:
\m ‘Mani iǧa SIDI, AREBBI nnec?’
\m Tiṭṭawin inu ad ɣares xzarent!
\m Řexxu ad tᵉttwaddez nettat,
\m am ubeǧaɛ di zznaqi.” \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Izhd. 79:10; 115:2; Yuw. 2:17\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Deg wass i di i ɣa ibna Netta
\m řeḥyuḍ nnec ɛawed,
\m deg wass nni ad iraḥ řḥeqq
\m ɣar řaggʷaj aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 12 Deg wass nni ad dd-asen,
\m zi Accur d tneddam n Miṣra,
\m u zi Miṣra ař iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*,
\m u zi řebḥar ař řebḥar
\m u zeg wedrar ař wedrar \add nneɣni.\add*
\m 
\v 13 \add Maca\add* ddunect ad tedweř
\m ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen,
\m zi ssibbet n imezdaɣ nnes,
\m zi ssibbet n řɣiǧet n tmegga nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt Irm. 21:14\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Arwes řgens nnec s teɣɣarct nnec,
\m uǧi n tesɣart nnec,
\m tenni iǧan weḥḥdes deg wezɣar,
\m di řwesṭ n Karmil.
\m Ejj i-tent ad arewsen di Bacan d Jilɛad,
\m am deg wussan n wecḥař uya. \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Mixa 5:3\x*
\m 
\v 15 Necc ad as sseccneɣ lmuɛjizat,
\m am deg wussan
\m řami dd-teffɣed zi temmurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 7:15 \xt Yuw. 2:26; 3:3. \x*
\m 
\v 16 Řegnus ad t twařin,
\m ad seḍḥan zi ssibbet
\m n marra tizemmar nsen,
\m nitni ad ssarsen afus x uqemmum,
\m imezzuɣen nsen ad dduhcaren.
\m 
\v 17 Nitni ad řesḥen taɛejjajt am ufiɣar,
\m ad dd-ffɣen zi lburjat nsen
\m am imuddar n temmurt ittbuɛen.
\m ad dd-asen ttarjijen
\m ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ,
\m u ad zzayek ggʷeden.” \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt Izhd. 72:9; Ica. 49:32\x*
\b
\s1 Tayri n Arebbi d arreḥmet nnes
\m 
\v 18 “Man wen iǧan d Arebbi am Cek,
\m wenni iɣeffaren řmuɛṣiyyet,
\m wenni iɛeddun x uxeṭṭu
\m n min iqqimen zi tesɣart nnes?
\m Netta war imenneɛ i řebda
\m deg weɣḍab nnes,
\m maɣar yarḍa as tamexsiwt icewwaren. \x ◘ \xo 7:18 \xt Uf. 34:6, 7; Izhd. 103:9\x*
\m 
\v 19 Netta ad xaneɣ yarḥem ɛawed,
\m Netta ad iɛfes x řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ,
\m \add wah\add*, Cek ad tenḍared
\m marra ddnub nsen
\m di řaǧaɣ n řebḥar.
\m 
\v 20 Iři Cek ad tessecned řaman i Yaɛqub
\m \add u\add* tamexsiwt icewwaren i Ibrahim,
\m am mammec tejjuǧed i řejdud nneɣ
\m zeg wussan n mecḥař uya.” 
